      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW LILIBET (6) could manage only fourth at Temora last time but impressed when clocking a dynamic 19.70 over 350m at this track the start prior. Expected to push the clock again here. PAW ZEVA (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.46) at this track behind Valedictorian in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Must be included in calculations. NITRO VENOM (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (20.29) in a Grade 4/5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Key player on best and worth another try. ALLERGY FREE (1) cannot be left out over a shorter trip.",
